# Birchwood

Personal full-stack portfolio website for exploring new technologies and 
platforms. Includes a microblog full-stack API and authentication API. Currently 
still in development.

## Project Structure

- [Backend](https://github.com/brandonapol/birchwood/tree/master/backend) is currently a Flask application. It has authentication routes completed and a very simple JSON API set up in preparation for pending front end.
- [Frontend](https://github.com/brandonapol/birchwood/tree/master/frontend/birchwood) is an in-process Vue app. It includes Tailwindcss and TypeScript and a Babel transpilation.

